      <title>日本区域性银行向大型银行支付市场招聘费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/japan-lender-ready-to-pay-megabank-salaries-for-market-hires</link>
      <description><![CDATA[山口金融集团是一家总部位于日本最大岛屿西端的区域性银行，该集团正考虑向拥有证券市场专业知识的新员工支付与该国最大银行员工相同的薪酬。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/japan-lender-ready-to-pay-megabank-salaries-for-market-hires</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 01:04:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
